8/25/2021

Instructions:

Part 1

Indicate the direction of the gap of the C using the arrow keys

A visual cue will indicate the next location of the target

Press any key to start


For the first task, you will be reporting the direction of the C/ where the gap is located. Keeping your focus on the middle of the screen should make this task easier. A small flashing circle located on the edge of the current target will appear in the direction that the next target will appear in. If this cue does not appear the location of the target will be the same. 

Part 2

For the second task, you will be reporting the direction of the C/ where the gap is located. Keeping your focus on the middle of the screen should make this task easier. There will not be a visual cue indicating the direction of the next target for this task. 
